Judy Pace https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Judy_Pace 0 Judy Lenteen Pace (born June 15, 1942) is an American actress. Pace is known for her roles in films and television shows, particularly blaxploitation films. Pace portrayed Vickie Fletcher on the TV series Peyton Place (1968-1969) and Pat Walters on the ABC drama series The Young Lawyers (1969-1971) for which she won an Image Award for Outstanding Actress in a Drama Series in 1970.
